data.description: Welcome to your new dream home, a hidden gem in the heart of Florida!  Located in the peaceful neighborhood of Countryside Forest, you will find the perfect blend of community activity with privacy all conveniently located to I-75. Here's a glimpse of what makes this property truly special:  Newer windows in the main house, installed in 2021. Enjoy natural light and energy efficiency!  A brand-new roof is currently in the works and will be completed before closing, ensuring your peace of mind and a secure future for your new home.  The living room boasts cathedral ceilings, creating a spacious and open atmosphere that's perfect for both relaxing and entertaining.  Step into the beautiful Florida room that extends off the family room, where you can savor the warmth and beauty of the Sunshine State year-round.  Coastal style remodeled kitchen with butcher block counter tops for all your culinary adventures!   The master suite is complete with a walk-in closet, a beautifully tiled shower, and new sliding door to the back yard, making every morning a spa-like experience.   The second bathroom is a haven for relaxation with its deep jacuzzi soaking tub, allowing you to unwind after a long day.  Enjoy the comfort of vinyl plank flooring in the main areas, while carpeting in the bedrooms adds a touch of coziness.  The converted garage adds a versatile fourth flex room, perfect for a home office, gym, or guest room. Plus, there's a step-down into a large, tiled laundry room, making chores a breeze.  Start your mornings right on the covered front porch with a charming swing, the perfect spot for your morning coffee or evening chats.  The privacy-fenced backyard with a storage shed is an excellent space for outdoor gatherings, gardening, or simply enjoying some fresh air.  The sellers are motivated, making this the perfect opportunity to make this property your own. Don't wait - seize the chance to create your Florida dream life! Schedule a private tour today and start envisioning your future in this beautiful home!
